snippet.title: D-Day Invasions - Releasing May 24th on Quest 2 & Quest 3
snippet.description:
Fight in online multiplayer battles with up to 64 players (32 on Quest) in chaotic battles.

There are five classes with a progression system allowing you to enhance each class with special abilities and perks. Weapons can be customized with a variety of attachments including scopes, grips, bayonets, weapon skins and more.

Online gameplay features epic matches with up to  64/32 players in multiple game modes including favorites such as Team Deathmatch, Attack & Defend and Free For All. 

PC VR and PS VR2 versions have optional 64 player matches on larger maps. When PC & PS VR2 versions enable crossplay with Quest players, matches will be limited to 32 players on smaller maps.

Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/des8fhgAPz
